    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="杂凑函数"><a href="#杂凑函数" class="headerlink" title="杂凑函数"></a>杂凑函数</h1><span id="more"></span><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115091834322.png" alt="image-20221115091834322" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115091947930.png" alt="image-20221115091947930" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115092146832.png" alt="image-20221115092146832" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p>强化md结构：</p><p>在分块的最后加消息长度</p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115092536650.png" alt="image-20221115092536650" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115092547654.png" alt="image-20221115092547654" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115150931232.png" alt="image-20221115150931232" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p>MD4算法：</p><p>输入的密钥（消息M），将512bit的消息块划分为16个32比特字，记为$m<em>0,m_1….m</em>{15}$, $w_j$为消息扩展的内容为48个</p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115154326462.png" alt="image-20221115154326462" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p>三个轮函数每16个换一个</p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115163415671.png" alt="image-20221115154412693" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p>输出值为T=(a+aa)||(b+bb)||(c+cc)||(d+dd)</p><p>aa||bb||cc||dd 为连接变量，初始为IV。</p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115160246771.png" alt="image-20221115160246771" style="zoom: 50%;" /></p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115162121336.png" alt="image-20221115162121336"></p><p>9</p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221115154412693.png" alt="image-20221115163415671" style="zoom:50%;" /></p>]]></content>
    
    
