    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Numpy对维数的理解"><a href="#Numpy对维数的理解" class="headerlink" title="Numpy对维数的理解"></a>Numpy对维数的理解</h1><span id="more"></span><p>对数组的某种特定元素进行操作，例如将小于0的元素变为0，等等。</p><p>例如：</p><figure class="highlight py"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a=np.where(a != <span class="number">0</span>, a, <span class="number">0.00001</span>)<span class="comment">#####将数组中为0的元素替换为0.00001</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>numpy.concatenate()</p><p>numpy.clip(a, a_min, a_max, out=None)[source]</p><p>clip这个函数将将数组中的元素限制在a_min, a_max之间，大于a_max的就使得它等于 a_max，小于a_min,的就使得它等于a_min。</p><p>numpy数组维度的理解</p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/Page3.jpg" alt="Page1"></p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/Page2.jpg" alt="Page2"></p><p><img src="https://wynneyin.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/Page1.jpg" alt="Page3"></p>]]></content>
    
    
